{"tid":1664014,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個小氣朋友","createTime":"2019-10-19T19:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T18:52:42.000Z","uid":289152,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"74d3ab1cd0cdf09cd9b3f1f566db60b42809e6dc","tid":1664014,"uid":289152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:13:31.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同朋友租屋住，簽左一年約，住左半年就無繼續住。租金連wifi錢，我應承繼續比，但唔住租金仲要比貴啲，電費仲要繼續收我。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電費佢要收我10%，但我已經搬走，無用到一度電費。佢論點係租屋包埋水電費，唔用都要照比。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原先3人租2房，我同另一個朋友share room比4500一個月，另一個比5000。一個月總租金為14000。後來我搬走，我同意要繼續比租金到租約期滿。但因為我搬走既關係，另外兩個既租金就必需相同先叫合理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我眼中認為既合理：<br />\n我照比4500，另外兩個朋友各比4750。<br />\n<br />\n朋友眼中認為既合理：<br />\n因為我搬走既關係，同我同房既伙伴，被迫變成住單人房，由租金4500變成4750，認為不公平。所以佢希望總數除3。即每人交4666.6666。<br />\n<br />\n我租金由原本4500變成4666，另外兩個就變左4667。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係我問題定佢小氣，婆那數都同我計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我已經繼續比筆租金，無話走左去，但問我拎番啲電費我真係唔理解。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b910bcb28b8606dc5b9fdb1e846589a9bd527ee","tid":1664014,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「文宣升級」巴士流動大字報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1662724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1662724</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wj3z6Ov.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwj3z6Ov.jpg&h=9f735918&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b6935e4fc3b1f17b33f911a72d22adfee83f01dc","tid":1664014,"uid":289152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2098ddb779a23a0f92b055f91d4bbf4ac4b256","tid":1664014,"uid":289152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:15:09.000Z","msg":"求分析 1/10"},{"pid":"d224ae2382d174bf89ed8e76a6184d8c4f86fbbc","tid":1664014,"uid":289152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:16:02.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"a5b34c3c56ea2a968f777c334dd6898685890697","tid":1664014,"uid":289152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:17:30.000Z","msg":"自推十"},{"pid":"afe31fa9bbe5c9a935d2c9578722314088cf7acf","tid":1664014,"uid":289152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:18:23.000Z","msg":"自推九"},{"pid":"07dd603143d3e1dfa0461d9c510483ce8e7c903f","tid":1664014,"uid":128111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74d3ab1cd0cdf09cd9b3f1f566db60b42809e6dc","tid":1664014,"uid":289152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:13:31.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同朋友租屋住，簽左一年約，住左半年就無繼續住。租金連wifi錢，我應承繼續比，但唔住租金仲要比貴啲，電費仲要繼續收我。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電費佢要收我10%，但我已經搬走，無用到一度電費。佢論點係租屋包埋水電費，唔用都要照比。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原先3人租2房，我同另一個朋友share room比4500一個月，另一個比5000。一個月總租金為14000。後來我搬走，我同意要繼續比租金到租約期滿。但因為我搬走既關係，另外兩個既租金就必需相同先叫合理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我眼中認為既合理：<br />\n我照比4500，另外兩個朋友各比4750。<br />\n<br />\n朋友眼中認為既合理：<br />\n因為我搬走既關係，同我同房既伙伴，被迫變成住單人房，由租金4500變成4750，認為不公平。所以佢希望總數除3。即每人交4666.6666。<br />\n<br />\n我租金由原本4500變成4666，另外兩個就變左4667。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係我問題定佢小氣，婆那數都同我計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我已經繼續比筆租金，無話走左去，但問我拎番啲電費我真係唔理解。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gi